<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c4">[٨٨٠) عمار والد منصور بن عمار الواعظ]</span><a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span class="c1">" أضعف من ولده منصور"</span>. <span class="c1">"الإصابة"</span> <span class="c2">(١/ ٥٢١)</span>.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span class="c4">[٨٨١) عمر بن إبراهيم بن خالد الكردي الهاشمي]</span><a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span><span class="c1">" ساقط"</span>. <span class="c1">"الإصابة"</span> <span class="c2">(٦/ ٨٨)</span>. <span class="c1">"أحد المتروكين"</span>. <span class="c1">"الإصابة"</span> <span class="c2">(١/ ٢٦٠)</span>.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span><span class="c1">"مذكور بوضع الحديث"</span>. <span class="c1">"الإصابة"</span> <span class="c2">(٦/ ٢٦٩)</span>. <span class="c1">"متهم بالكذب"</span>. <span class="c1">"الإصابة"</span> <span class="c2">(٣/ ٤٨٣)</span>. <span class="c1">"كذاب"</span>. <span class="c1">"الدراية"</span> <span class="c2">(٢/ ١٤٨)</span>.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
